import { typographyMixin } from './typographyMixin';

export const predefinedMixins = {
  xxl: {
    regular: typographyMixin('xxl', 'regular'),
    contrastInvert: typographyMixin('xxl', 'contrastInvert'),
    overlay: typographyMixin('xxl', 'overlay'),
    overlayInvert: typographyMixin('xxl', 'overlayInvert'),
  },
  xl: {
    regular: typographyMixin('xl', 'regular'),
    contrastInvert: typographyMixin('xl', 'contrastInvert'),
    overlay: typographyMixin('xl', 'overlay'),
    overlayInvert: typographyMixin('xl', 'overlayInvert'),
  },
  lg: {
    regular: typographyMixin('lg', 'regular'),
    contrastInvert: typographyMixin('lg', 'contrastInvert'),
    overlay: typographyMixin('lg', 'overlay'),
    overlayInvert: typographyMixin('lg', 'overlayInvert'),
  },
  md: {
    highContrast: typographyMixin('md', 'highContrast'),
    regular: typographyMixin('md', 'regular'),
    lowContrast: typographyMixin('md', 'lowContrast'),
    url: typographyMixin('md', 'url'),
    success: typographyMixin('md', 'success'),
    warning: typographyMixin('md', 'warning'),
    error: typographyMixin('md', 'error'),
    contrastInvert: typographyMixin('md', 'contrastInvert'),
    overlay: typographyMixin('md', 'overlay'),
    overlayInvert: typographyMixin('md', 'overlayInvert'),
  },
  sm: {
    highContrast: typographyMixin('sm', 'highContrast'),
    regular: typographyMixin('sm', 'regular'),
    lowContrast: typographyMixin('sm', 'lowContrast'),
    url: typographyMixin('sm', 'url'),
    success: typographyMixin('sm', 'success'),
    warning: typographyMixin('sm', 'warning'),
    error: typographyMixin('sm', 'error'),
    contrastInvert: typographyMixin('sm', 'contrastInvert'),
    overlay: typographyMixin('sm', 'overlay'),
    overlayInvert: typographyMixin('sm', 'overlayInvert'),
  },
  xs: {
    highContrast: typographyMixin('xs', 'highContrast'),
    regular: typographyMixin('xs', 'regular'),
    lowContrast: typographyMixin('xs', 'lowContrast'),
    disabled: typographyMixin('xs', 'disabled'),
    url: typographyMixin('xs', 'url'),
    success: typographyMixin('xs', 'success'),
    warning: typographyMixin('xs', 'warning'),
    error: typographyMixin('xs', 'error'),
    contrastInvert: typographyMixin('xs', 'contrastInvert'),
    overlay: typographyMixin('xs', 'overlay'),
    overlayInvert: typographyMixin('xs', 'overlayInvert'),
  },
  xxs: {
    highContrast: typographyMixin('xxs', 'highContrast'),
    regular: typographyMixin('xxs', 'regular'),
    lowContrast: typographyMixin('xxs', 'lowContrast'),
    disabled: typographyMixin('xxs', 'disabled'),
    url: typographyMixin('xxs', 'url'),
    success: typographyMixin('xxs', 'success'),
    warning: typographyMixin('xxs', 'warning'),
    error: typographyMixin('xxs', 'error'),
    contrastInvert: typographyMixin('xxs', 'contrastInvert'),
    overlay: typographyMixin('xxs', 'overlay'),
    overlayInvert: typographyMixin('xxs', 'overlayInvert'),
  },
};
